        <mattext texttype="text/html">&lt;h1&gt;Session 22 Quiz – Local Storage and Game Persistence&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Test your understanding of localStorage API, JSON serialization, and data persistence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Topics Covered:&lt;/strong&gt;
- localStorage.setItem and getItem
- JSON.stringify and JSON.parse
- Type conversion with localStorage
- Error handling for storage
- Game state serialization&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instructions:&lt;/strong&gt;
